*******************************************************************************
	DESCRIPTION
*******************************************************************************

This software allows you to create and edit bookmarks on existing pdf files.

Installers will be available for linux and windows, while other operating 
systems users can download the zip archive version, i remind you that this 
is a java program so you need a Java Runtime Environment (version 6 or later) 
to run it.

To use the linux installer remember to give the downloaded file execution 
permissions, this can be done right clicking on it and choosing properties on 
most desktop environments or with the command:

chmod +x jpdfbookmarks-x.x.x-Linux-x86-Install

On Windows you should be able to launch the installer with a double click.

